{{intro|
This request is too difficult and is unlikely to be resolved through free forum discussions anywhere on the internet, including {{project_name_short}} forums.
}}

* '''Free support unlikely''': Based on past experience, it is highly unlikely that asking in free forums will result in support for an issue this complex. Solving this kind of problem often requires a great deal of time to fully understand the issue, design a dependable solution, and help with implementation. That level of effort is usually too large to expect from unpaid forum support. Community members may still try to help, but it would not be realistic to expect a complete solution this way.
* '''Risk of recommending an external IT development or support company''': Even if a user finds a contractor with the right expertise, there are still important risks. Miscommunication, unclear expectations, or incomplete project planning can lead to poor results, disappointment, and frustration for everyone involved. In the worst case, this may also lead to unfair blame being directed at related tools or platforms such as {{project_name_short}}, which can harm trust in the community.
* '''Pricing expectations''': Projects of this kind are usually expensive. In rare cases, some work might be available for a few hundred USD, but a dependable and well-tested solution is more likely to cost thousands of USD. Many users understandably do not realize in advance how difficult or costly such work can be. This can lead to surprise, frustration, or disagreement once realistic market pricing becomes clear.
* '''Unsuitable suggestions''': Suggestions such as crowdfunding or bounties may sound simple, but in practice they are not simple to organize or manage either. They come with their own challenges, limitations, and risks. See also {{kicksecure_wiki
|wikipage=Dev/Open_Source_Business_Models
|text=Open Source Business Models
}}, {{kicksecure_wiki
|wikipage=Dev/Open_Source_Business_Models#Crowdfunding_Model
|text=Crowdfunding Model
}} and {{kicksecure_wiki
|wikipage=Dev/bounty
|text=Development Bounties
}}.
* '''Outlook''': This response is not meant to discourage curiosity, learning, or experimentation. Its purpose is to set realistic expectations about the level of expertise, time, and funding that would be required. Anyone who wants to pursue this should be prepared for a significant investment of effort and possibly substantial financial cost.

